{
  "stem": "12051.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were terribly afraid to go in there, that it's a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But you had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You went in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And you had to register.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And to-- they told you, everything you have, you have to give them, all your clothes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then you go into showers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You walked into one door, and you stood naked there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And on the other side, they gave you some clothes full of blood that wasn't yours.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It doesn't matter because that was clothes that they have killed already people before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So they gave it to you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But as I walked in into that tremendous room, I saw a lot of women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there was a transport that came from another camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There were 2,000 women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Among them was my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I found my mother there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And, I don't know, at that age, it was difficult for anybody to understand that I was that lucky to find my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I took over, like she would be my child and I was the mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Wherever we-- you had to stand in the morning at 5 o'clock at an Appell.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So I used to pinch her cheeks, that she should have a little color, that they shouldn't call her out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, I brought her into the camp from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Also, I went to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I begged them they should give her permission, that she is a young woman-- she was 35 years old-- that she's still capable of working, that they should let her stay in camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they gave me that permission, and she stayed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But then we were separated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Here, I found her again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I took over.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every time there was an Appell, they told me-- told my mother, oh, you step back.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
